  "3145480": {
    "name": "喵与时光的街角",
    "steam_appid": 3145480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个美丽的小镇上，扮演并体验猫咪的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/3e66684284ff5724deb4cf424702bf7c.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/0643359cc21ad17ce340a250736df6ed.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/e1a1b1a0ed746c4707048c471afe4cef.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/e513fe82e1c667b5257f4886458b2088.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/a7a052ff086a0c5ee1ed5fa49c2e9033.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[猫的生活]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要翻找垃圾桶和回收箱，发现各种食物。记住那些会有食物的地点，在饥饿来临的时候去碰碰运气。你还要随时关注天气，下雨会使小猫的体力迅速流失，及时寻找可以避雨的屋檐，保持小猫的身体干爽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/4382a8312f1efaccc06919da59e754ec.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[猫的故事]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >饭团屋的饭团女士偶尔会给流浪小猫提供任务，帮助她完成，会触发全新的情节。还有小镇上生活着的其他小猫，彼此之间也会发生有趣的事情。偶尔与路人互动一下，或者找到隐藏的地点，也会发生一些令人感动的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/24ea7bd2e921198698260247d2e660f0.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[小游戏与收集]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有空的时候可以挑战钓鱼小游戏或者是玩球的小游戏，取胜就能获得不错的奖励。还有许多猫咪硬币不时出现在各个地方，收集它们，然后前往自动贩卖机就可以抽取各种神奇的能力或者是额外的食物。在计划一次活动之前，不妨先通过自动贩卖机和猫咪硬币，增强一下自己的能力或者让一整天都不会下雨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/7dfe2fd55bdf51a4878bbb25617a5ff0.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[猫的交通]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主干道两侧都有猫咪专用的高速通道，在高速通道上奔跑，速度会大幅提升，能够节省不少移动时间。通过运动，也能够改善猫咪的速度。要留意经过小镇的卡车，如果撞上去，可是会直接死亡的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/70dfb070267102ce46e0e85ddb67a0e5.avif?t=1761974244\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[猫的伙伴]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将获得一位可怜的小伙伴，在游戏中，你不仅要关注自己的状态，还要负责照顾它，通过温暖的对话鼓励它活下去，帮助它找到走失的家人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/fa14d2df20772c371d9d8117c78db4c5.avif?t=1761974244\" width=95 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你曾经不知道它们在想什么，为什么要那样做，现在你将有机会了解。成为一只真正的猫咪，体验生存的艰辛，也找到心中对生活的热爱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145480/extras/2d119af908b33f360056e888c1507e98.avif?t=1761974244\" width=800 height=322 /></span></p>",
